text.tspan: “Time is money.” For the industry training designers,
they usually have a time limitation to deliver the
training. For the learners, they also have little extra
time to learn besides their work.
Time constraint is the biggest challenge.
Learners address that real-world scenario is their
biggest motivation. For example, troubleshooting
for customers is an important part of some learners
work. The ACE training is supposed to help with it.
Real-world scenario is the essential
motivation for learning.
Customization is useful but challenging to develop.
Learners want customization or even personalization
and PMs also knew it’s valueable. But which element
we choose to make it customized is vital otherwise
the implementation will be challenging.
Customization is achievable now in the
webinar but high-cost to implement.
Trainers have mandated content to cover so the
current training is overwhelmed due to the long
time duration, big topics, and hands-on demo in
webinar. But learners want more skills and tailored
content delivery.
Emphasize on skills taught, not content
covered.
